divs: Sighting DetailsHello, My Husband and I were sightseeing along the pacific coast highway on Saturday, July 11, 2009. We noticed some windsurfers and stopped the car on the side of the road and got out to take this picture. I sensed something. I have always been interested in ufo's. We noticed the two disc shaped objects above the windsurfers when we put them on the computer after we got home to Dickinson, North Dakota. Seeing these two objects just made my day! I would like to share this picture with anyone interested in ufo's. Thank you!
